  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/50px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/75px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/100px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Durran XXI Durrandon</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/50px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/75px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/100px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Reign</th><td>\nDuring the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_Invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal Invasion\">Andal Invasion</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nDurran XXI Durrandon</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Durran XXI Durrandon</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_Invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal Invasion\">Andal Invasion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Durran_XXI_Durrandon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>, he sought out the remaining <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_Forest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Children of the Forest\">Children of the Forest</a> taking refuge in caves and hollow hills, and made common cause with them. This <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood_Alliance\" title=\"Weirwood Alliance\">Weirwood Alliance</a> dealt the <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a> a series of stinging defeats in such battles as the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_Black_Bog\" title=\"Battle at Black Bog\">Battle at Black Bog</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_in_the_Misty_Wood&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Battle in the Misty Wood (page does not exist)\">Battle in the Misty Wood</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_beneath_the_Howling_Hill&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Battle beneath the Howling Hill (page does not exist)\">Battle beneath the Howling Hill</a>, and checked the decline of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_the_Storm\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kingdom of the Storm\">Kingdom of the Storm</a> for a time.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Durran_XXI_Durrandon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B